    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Watch as our hero takes on a powerful forest beast in real-time combat! In <i>Galactic Heroes: The Enchanted Forest</i>, every encounter counts — use your reflexes and skills to defeat enemies, survive tough battles, and clear the level. With each fight, you get one step closer to restoring balance to the enchanted world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122500/extras/daee9d0c9093528bab42bf1e3dfef445.poster.avif?t=1763488810\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122500/extras/daee9d0c9093528bab42bf1e3dfef445.webm?t=1763488810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122500/extras/daee9d0c9093528bab42bf1e3dfef445.mp4?t=1763488810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🐎 Ride into Battle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mount up and dominate the battlefield! In Galactic Heroes: The Enchanted Forest, riding animals isn't just for travel — it's a powerful tool in combat and strategy. Whether you’re charging into enemy lines or chasing down elusive foes, mounted units bring speed, strength, and style to your adventure.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each rideable creature has unique advantages.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122500/extras/e26e40355efd970e2335fd2bddabcf22.poster.avif?t=1763488810\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122500/extras/e26e40355efd970e2335fd2bddabcf22.webm?t=1763488810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122500/extras/e26e40355efd970e2335fd2bddabcf22.mp4?t=1763488810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >❤️ United in Battle: Meet Luna</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not<strong> all heroes walk alone. In <i>Galactic Heroes: The Enchanted Forest</i>, the journey is shared. Luna, the hero’s loyal companion and love interest, fights alongside you as you both venture deep into the forest’s mysteries.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Together, you’ll face powerful enemies, uncover hidden secrets, and protect each other in the face of danger. Their bond isn’t just emotional — it’s tactical, with coordinated attacks and teamwork that turn the tide of battle.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122500/extras/f5505f19e3e3234c4514cc8455899f42.poster.avif?t=1763488810\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122500/extras/f5505f19e3e3234c4514cc8455899f42.webm?t=1763488810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122500/extras/f5505f19e3e3234c4514cc8455899f42.mp4?t=1763488810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
